  <catch_line/>
  <text>While doing business as a trading stamp company in the State, a trading stamp company may not:<section prefix=""><section prefix="(1)">commit fraud;</section><section prefix="(2)">make a false representation; or</section><section prefix="(3)">use a lottery.</section></section></text>
